## Step ## Step 6: Calculate the percentage of patients with regular heartbeat and low blood pressure
Given that 19% have low blood pressure and $3.9\%$ have irregular heartbeat and low blood pressure, the percentage with regular heartbeat and low blood pressure is $19\% - 3.9\% = 15.1\%$.

